---
title: Char Siu Chicken & Udon Noodle Broth with Garlic Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: If you need any way to change up a chicken and udon noodle broth, you can’t go wrong with a coating of char siu. The chicken is instantly wrapped in rich flavours and combine with the sesame-soy broth for a bowl that is purely delicious.
